tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE PatientData (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    medical_condition VARCHAR(50),
    telemedicine_usage BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name TEXT,
  age INT,
  gender TEXT,
  diagnosis TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE health_records (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  date DATE,
  temperature FLOAT,
  heart_rate INT,
  blood_pressure TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE telemedicine_records (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  appointment_date DATE,
  diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
  prescription VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50),
  date_of_birth DATE,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  address VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE medical_records (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
  consultation_date DATE,
  doctor_name VARCHAR(50),
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE telemedicine_sessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  consultation_type VARCHAR(50),
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Patient (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(50),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  city VARCHAR(50),
  insurance VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE MedicalRecord (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
  treatment VARCHAR(100),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE TelemedicineUsage (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  physician_id INT,
  duration_minutes INT,
  consultation_type VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE PublicHealthData (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  city VARCHAR(50),
  population INT,
  health_index INT,
  last_updated DATE
);

CREATE TABLE ResearchStudy (
  study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  study_name VARCHAR(100),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  description TEXT,
  lead_researcher VARCHAR(50)
);
